{"tid":1691751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有手足去咗意大利同法國做文宣","createTime":"2019-11-03T19:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:51:11.000Z","uid":8030,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"766df91b0f9da8bf97722c0b9277cb1859aa8f55","tid":1691751,"uid":8030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T19:10:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24514/831%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-24541/831%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7-90%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9C%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AA%E6%AD%BB%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%9A%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F24514%2F831%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2582%2598%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595-%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590-24541%2F831%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25AB%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E5%2582%25B7-90%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%259A%259F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=95565900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24514/831%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E6%89%93%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90-24541/831%E5%A4%AA%E5%AD%90%E7%AB%99%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7-90%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%81%9C%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AA%E6%AD%BB%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E5%9A%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n係10.31眾新聞出咗一份831手足專訪，原來手足曾經出國到訪意大利同法國做文宣。發現手足喺意大利向siena同florence既國際特赦組織分享香港既情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Oq5k4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Oq5k4p.jpg&h=95a3a553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4AOZqv9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4AOZqv9.jpg&h=5f8986d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OjZBsKy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOjZBsKy.jpg&h=dcf1701e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而喺法國根據居法港人組織Comit&eacute; pour la libert&eacute; &agrave; HK情報，手足曾經同佢地見過歐洲議會議員Pascal Durand及Bernard Guetta，而眾志成員黃奕武加入後者既會面，仲同巴黎特赦組織及法國工會Solidaires講述香港情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後發現喺Extinction Rebellion同黃背心合作既佔領運作當中曾經有港人聲援，相信亦都係依位手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20191006/s00005/1570371989309/%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%97%E5%91%BD-%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4-%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%93%AC%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00005%2F1570371989309%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2597%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=8e87d482\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20191006%2Fs00005%2F1570371989309%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%258A%2597%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BD%2594%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4-%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF&h=30060169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20191006/s00005/1570371989309/%E7%92%B0%E4%BF%9D%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E6%8A%97%E5%91%BD-%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4-%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%93%AC%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n佔領直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1476458045863584&amp;id=345110412254517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1476458045863584%26id%3D345110412254517&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=ec8c8e52\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1476458045863584&amp;id=345110412254517</a><br />\n其實由此可見，前線唔一定要同文宣分開，因為前線既分享往往係更貼地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFB專頁 居法港人組織 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKparapluies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKparapluies%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=770a03f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKparapluies/</a>"},{"pid":"2ad0b80ddb3464e63fa75a957c05d867d03c0572","tid":1691751,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"甴近平<br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-au